Control freaks have taken away many liberties in the fight against Covid-19. The proposed 8pm to 5am curfew is a step too far. We are entitled to better explanations. Covid-19 cannot be a blanket excuse to cover every tyrannical diktat – petty or otherwise – from prohibiting pavement clean-ups, to banning all alcohol sales. Why is a curfew necessary when we move from Level 5 lockdown to a supposedly more relaxed Level 4? We have survived nearly five weeks without a curfew, why impose one now? Under lockdown we are already confined to our homes, except when on “essential” tasks....